CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 7, 1958, pg. A12 reads: "Capital Charmers - Washington (D.C.) Gays' delegation included Frankie Deane, Ruth Whitted, Bertha Bolden, Grace Drew. Fourth from left is Evelyn Johnson, Aliquippa.  Far Right: Lucille Cole of Pittsburgh."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of six Gay Northeasterner members, Frankie Deane, Ruth Whitted, Bertha Bolden, Evelyn Johnson, Grace Drew, and Lucille Cole, standing in hallway of Penn Sheraton Hotel for grand ball
